<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ArrayOfTableExplain xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>#iID$0</Column>
		<Text>战斗编码</Text>
		<Explain>战斗编码；与剧情等文件的触发战斗关联</Explain>
		<IsSelColumn>1</IsSelColumn>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sAreaID$1</Column>
		<Text>战斗地图编码</Text>
		<Explain>战斗地图编码；（mapid_场景代号）</Explain>
		<IsSelColumn>1</IsSelColumn>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sMustJoinStaff$2</Column>
		<Text>必须参战人员</Text>
		<Explain>必须参战人员；格式为（加入回合数，battlecharacter代码，阵营代码）阵营代码0为己方，每个数字代表一个阵营</Explain>
		<IsSelColumn>1</IsSelColumn>
		<Width>745</Width>
		<Height>63</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sJoinStaff$3</Column>
		<Explain>和smustjoinstaff一样则不能配置队友，填0则可以。</Explain>
		<Width>745</Width>
		<Height>63</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>iVictory$4</Column>
		<Text>胜利条件</Text>
		<Explain>胜利条件；（1，x，0）代表x回合后胜利，（0,0,0）对方全灭，（0，x，0）x回合自动胜利</Explain>
		<Width>315</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>iFale$5</Column>
		<Text>失败条件</Text>
		<Explain>失败条件；（1，x，0）代表x回合后失败，（0,0,0）我放全灭，（2，npcid，0）npc死后失败，（0，x，0）x回合自动失败</Explain>
		<Width>530</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sReward$6</Column>
		<Text>胜利奖励及后续；rewarddata.txt</Text>
		<Explain>胜利奖励；rewarddata.txt</Explain>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sReward$7</Column>
		<Text>失败奖励及后续；rewarddata.txt</Text>
		<Explain>失败奖励；rewarddata.txt</Explain>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sTime$8</Column>
		<Explain>战场时间；对应1-24小时，战斗中的光照条件随按照时辰会发生变化（改成0的话直接就黑了），-1为不改变当前时间</Explain>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sBGM$9</Column>
		<Explain>背景音乐；格式为Story_两位数序号</Explain>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sinside$10</Column>
		<Explain>是否在室内；1是0否，似乎室内战斗不计算时间流动</Explain>
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
	<TableExplain>
		<Column>sautosave$11</Column>
		<Text />
		<Explain />
		<Width>100</Width>
		<Height>21</Height>
	</TableExplain>
</ArrayOfTableExplain>